00:08:46.630 --> 00:08:49.049 line:90% position:50% align:center
Max and I changed our approach.

00:08:53.011 --> 00:08:55.639 line:90% position:50% align:center
We found out what mattered to our kids

00:08:57.140 --> 00:08:58.809 line:90% position:50% align:center
—like friends,

00:09:00.894 --> 00:09:03.730 line:90% position:50% align:center
. . . adjusting to a blended family,

00:09:05.899 --> 00:09:08.068 line:90% position:50% align:center
. . . dating.

00:09:14.324 --> 00:09:16.535 line:90% position:50% align:center
So we turned things around
and used family worship

00:09:16.535 --> 00:09:19.830 line:90% position:50% align:center
to focus on what our kids really needed

00:09:34.136 --> 00:09:36.763 line:90% position:50% align:center
and to prepare ourselves
for possible future trials.

00:09:51.945 --> 00:09:52.904 line:90% position:50% align:center
Good night, y’all.

00:09:52.904 --> 00:09:53.989 line:90% position:50% align:center
Good night.

