Um,

00:09:58.869 --> 00:10:01.329 line:90% position:50% align:center
family worship was—was cool.

00:10:01.329 --> 00:10:03.623 line:90% position:50% align:center
It was.

00:10:03.623 --> 00:10:05.750 line:90% position:50% align:center
I’m glad you liked it.

00:10:05.750 --> 00:10:07.043 line:90% position:50% align:center
Thank you.

00:10:07.043 --> 00:10:08.211 line:90% position:50% align:center
Good night, y’all.

00:10:08.211 --> 00:10:08.879 line:90% position:50% align:center
Night.

00:10:08.879 --> 00:10:10.630 line:90% position:50% align:center
