00:10:24.603 --> 00:10:25.770 line:90% position:50% align:center
Thanks.

00:10:28.106 --> 00:10:29.983 line:90% position:50% align:center
Aww, congratulations.

00:10:29.983 --> 00:10:31.193 line:90% position:50% align:center
Thank you.

00:10:33.528 --> 00:10:36.406 line:90% position:50% align:center
Hey, it’s selfie time, everybody.
Come on, let’s get together.

00:10:36.406 --> 00:10:39.201 line:90% position:50% align:center
All right. On three
we’re going to say Bethel, OK?

00:10:39.201 --> 00:10:40.619 line:90% position:50% align:center
All right.

00:10:40.619 --> 00:10:43.163 line:90% position:50% align:center
