00:10:43.163 --> 00:10:45.332 line:90% position:50% align:center
Bethel!

00:11:04.643 --> 00:11:07.145 line:90% position:50% align:center
We’ve come a long way.

00:11:18.907 --> 00:11:20.659 line:90% position:50% align:center
And through it all,

00:11:20.659 --> 00:11:22.786 line:90% position:50% align:center
Jehovah has taught us to love

00:11:23.995 --> 00:11:26.498 line:90% position:50% align:center
and he’s given our family

00:11:26.498 --> 00:11:27.999 line:90% position:50% align:center
peace.

00:12:41.031 --> 00:12:45.076 line:90% position:50% align:center
We can see that Max and Irene analyzed
what was wrong with family worship

00:12:45.076 --> 00:12:48.121 line:90% position:50% align:center
and decided to change their approach.

00:12:48.121 --> 00:12:52.459 line:90% position:50% align:center
Let’s examine how they did that
and what it means for us.

00:12:52.459 --> 00:12:55.128 line:90% position:50% align:center
What did they do to make their

00:12:55.128 --> 00:12:57.839 line:90% position:50% align:center
family worship more meaningful?

00:12:57.839 --> 00:13:00.717 line:90% position:50% align:center
Well, Max and Irene had to ask themselves

00:13:00.717 --> 00:13:03.428 line:90% position:50% align:center
what was going on in their kids’ lives.

00:13:03.428 --> 00:13:06.640 line:90% position:50% align:center
What topics could they
discuss at family worship

00:13:06.640 --> 00:13:09.601 line:90% position:50% align:center
that would truly be useful to their kids?

00:13:09.601 --> 00:13:13.188 line:90% position:50% align:center
Did you smile when you saw Max
almost drop the glass

00:13:13.188 --> 00:13:16.024 line:90% position:50% align:center
when his daughter talked about dating?

00:13:16.024 --> 00:13:19.235 line:90% position:50% align:center
But what a difference their efforts to listen

00:13:19.235 --> 00:13:21.488 line:90% position:50% align:center
and really understand what was happening

00:13:21.488 --> 00:13:24.824 line:90% position:50% align:center
with the kids made in the family worship!

00:13:24.824 --> 00:13:29.454 line:90% position:50% align:center
How did Max and Irene
make family worship more enjoyable?

00:13:29.454 --> 00:13:33.625 line:90% position:50% align:center
Did you see how the family
was reacting at family worship now?

00:13:33.625 --> 00:13:35.627 line:90% position:50% align:center
What a difference!

00:13:35.627 --> 00:13:37.671 line:90% position:50% align:center
The kids were smiling.

00:13:37.671 --> 00:13:39.881 line:90% position:50% align:center
They looked engaged in the discussion

00:13:39.881 --> 00:13:43.176 line:90% position:50% align:center
and touched by what they were discussing.

00:13:43.176 --> 00:13:46.388 line:90% position:50% align:center
So do what you can
to make sure that your family

00:13:46.388 --> 00:13:48.682 line:90% position:50% align:center
feels relaxed and happy

00:13:48.682 --> 00:13:51.059 line:90% position:50% align:center
and that your family worship reflects

00:13:51.059 --> 00:13:54.187 line:90% position:50% align:center
the kind of happy
and joyful God that Jehovah is.

00:13:54.187 --> 00:13:57.190 line:90% position:50% align:center
Remember, your family will often remember

00:13:57.190 --> 00:14:00.360 line:90% position:50% align:center
more about how they felt
during family worship

00:14:00.360 --> 00:14:03.905 line:90% position:50% align:center
than maybe the exact details
of what they learned.

00:14:05.490 --> 00:14:07.909 line:90% position:50% align:center
Keep worshipping Jehovah as a family.

00:14:07.909 --> 00:14:10.286 line:90% position:50% align:center
Make your family worship consistent,

00:14:10.286 --> 00:14:12.872 line:90% position:50% align:center
enjoyable, and meaningful.

00:14:12.872 --> 00:14:16.960 line:90% position:50% align:center
And work together to overcome obstacles,

00:14:16.960 --> 00:14:21.923 line:90% position:50% align:center
just like Max and Irene and the kids
all worked together to solve problems

00:14:21.923 --> 00:14:24.968 line:90% position:50% align:center
and create a very peaceful family life.

00:14:24.968 --> 00:14:27.512 line:90% position:50% align:center
It was really beautiful to see how far

00:14:27.512 --> 00:14:30.014 line:90% position:50% align:center
they had come by applying Bible principles.

00:14:31.391 --> 00:14:34.602 line:90% position:50% align:center
In review, this symposium has taught us

00:14:34.602 --> 00:14:36.855 line:90% position:50% align:center
that Bible principles can be used

00:14:36.855 --> 00:14:40.024 line:90% position:50% align:center
as a road map to family peace.

00:14:40.024 --> 00:14:42.944 line:90% position:50% align:center
Work hard to show love and respect,

00:14:42.944 --> 00:14:46.823 line:90% position:50% align:center
to improve communication,
to work together as a team,

00:14:46.823 --> 00:14:50.118 line:90% position:50% align:center
and to worship Jehovah together.

00:14:50.118 --> 00:14:53.705 line:90% position:50% align:center
And please be patient with one another

00:14:53.705 --> 00:14:57.083 line:90% position:50% align:center
as you form habits that lead to peace.

00:14:57.083 --> 00:14:59.419 line:90% position:50% align:center
With Jehovah’s help, you and your family

00:14:59.419 --> 00:15:03.131 line:90% position:50% align:center
will enjoy peace that only he can provide.

